#   BRO — pager / hunk-renderer tickets

[Bro] is the interactive pager and the **shared hunk renderer**: every
projector (`log`/`status`/`grep`/`diff`/`commit`/`blame`…) emits `dog/HUNK`
streams that bro renders. Tickets here improve that rendering — presentation
is bro's job, producers only emit `{ts,verb,uri}`+body. Method: [Issues].

